---
import '../styles/tokens.css';
import GlobalNav from '../components/GlobalNav.astro';
import AllYieldsPanel from '../components/AllYieldsPanel.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Why this exists. — OurOrigin</title>
    
    <meta name="description" content="OurOrigin exists because the people and places behind real products deserve to be seen, not kept in the background of a marketing story.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://ourorigin.in/why">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Why this exists. | OurOrigin">
    <meta property="og:description" content="A small business sourcing from the Western Ghats. We show you the origin and let you reach your own conclusions.">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://ourorigin.in/why">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://ourorigin.in/og-image.jpg">

    <!-- Google Fonts with display=swap as explicitly requested -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400..900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: var(--color-forest-deep);
            color: var(--color-warm-cream);
            height: 100%;
        }
        .page-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20vh 5vw;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        p {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .nav-link {
            font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
            color: var(--color-warm-cream);
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            display: inline-block;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 241, 235, 0.3);
            padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
            align-self: flex-start;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            border-bottom-color: var(--color-warm-cream);
        }
        .fssai-footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding-top: 4rem;
            font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--color-warm-cream);
            opacity: 0.4;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <GlobalNav />
    <AllYieldsPanel />
    <main id="main-content" class="page-container">
        <h1>Why this exists.</h1>
        
        <p>A label says what something is. It rarely says where — not the place, not the soil, not the season, not the person. Not the thing behind the thing.</p>
        
        <p>We source from the Western Ghats because we believe those hidden layers are the most interesting part. The people and places behind real products deserve to be seen, not kept in the background of a marketing story.</p>
        
        <p>We don't make claims about sustainability or ethics or purity. We show you the origin and let you reach your own conclusions.</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="nav-link">Return to the Matrix</a>
        
        <div class="fssai-footer">FSSAI Reg. No. 21326135000354</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
